-- Pernod Ricard Sales Rebound on Hotel, Restaurant Demand, La Lettre Reports
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-09-27T05:26:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-27/pernod-ricard-sales-rebound-on-hotel-restaurant-demand-la-lettre-reports.html
Pernod Ricard SA had an increase in
summer sales of 7 percent versus 2008, La Lettre de L’Expansion
reported, without citing anyone.  The company benefited from a recovery in demand in cafes,
hotels and restaurants, according to the weekly newsletter,
which didn’t define the dates of the summer period.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  